44struct OpData {
45 // Which kernel type to use. Full kernel (24 inputs) or basic kernel (5
46 // inputs).
47 // Please note the 20-input full kernel is deprecated and only kept
48 // here for backward compatibility.
49 TfLiteLSTMKernelType kernel_type;
50
51 // If the lstm is layer norm.
52 bool use_layer_norm;
53
54 // These fields are only used by full kernel.
55 int scratch_tensor_index;
56 lstm_eval::IntegerLstmParameter integer_lstm_param;
57 bool compute_row_sums;
58
59 // Only used for sparse hybrid lstm kernels.
60 int ledger_index;
61 bool ledger_initialized;
62};

68enum HybridTemporaryTensor {

78 kInputZeroPoints = 9,

81 kNumHybridTemporaryTensors = 12,

84constexpr int kLedgersToAdd = 9;
85constexpr int kInputToInputWeightsLedgerOffset = 0;
86constexpr int kInputToForgetWeightsLedgerOffset = 1;
87constexpr int kInputToCellWeightsLedgerOffset = 2;
88constexpr int kInputToOutputWeightsLedgerOffset = 3;
89constexpr int kRecurrentToInputWeightsLedgerOffset = 4;
90constexpr int kRecurrentToForgetWeightsLedgerOffset = 5;

93constexpr int kProjectionWeightsLedgerOffset = 8;

95TfLiteStatus make_ledger(const TfLiteSparsity* sparsity, TfLiteContext* context,
96 TfLiteTensor* ledger) {
97 ledger->type = kTfLiteUInt8;
98 ledger->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRwPersistent;
99 if (sparsity == nullptr) {
100 return kTfLiteOk;
101 }
102 TfLiteIntArray* ledger_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(1);
103 ledger_size->data[0] = sparsity->dim_metadata[1].array_indices->size +
104 sparsity->dim_metadata[1].array_segments->size - 1;
105 return context->ResizeTensor(context, ledger, ledger_size);
106}
107
108TfLiteStatus copy_ledger(const TfLiteSparsity* sparsity, TfLiteTensor* ledger) {
109 if (sparsity == nullptr) {
110 return kTfLiteOk;
111 }
112
113 const auto* array_segments = sparsity->dim_metadata[1].array_segments;
114 const auto* array_indices = sparsity->dim_metadata[1].array_indices;
115 uint8_t* output_data = GetTensorData<uint8_t>(ledger);
116 int output_data_ptr = 0;
117
118 for (int i = 0; i < array_segments->size - 1; i++) {
119 int row_start = array_segments->data[i];
120 int row_end = array_segments->data[i + 1];
121 if (row_end - row_start > UINT8_MAX) {
122 return kTfLiteError;
123 }
124 // Copy num of non-zero blocks in row i.
125 output_data[output_data_ptr] = static_cast<uint8_t>(row_end - row_start);
126 output_data_ptr++;
127
128 for (int j = row_start; j < row_end; j++) {
129 if (array_indices->data[j] > UINT8_MAX) {
130 return kTfLiteError;
131 }
132 // Copy indices of non-zero blocks in row i.
133 output_data[output_data_ptr] =
134 static_cast<uint8_t>(array_indices->data[j]);
135 output_data_ptr++;
136 }
137 }
138 return kTfLiteOk;
139}
140
141TfLiteStatus PopulateQuantizedLstmParams8x8_16(
142 TfLiteContext* context, TfLiteNode* node,
143 lstm_eval::IntegerLstmParameter* integer_lstm_param) {
144 // Calculate quantized clip for projection and cell.
145 const auto* params = static_cast<TfLiteLSTMParams*>(node->builtin_data);
146 const float cell_clip = params->cell_clip;
147 const float proj_clip = params->proj_clip;
148
149 const TfLiteTensor* cell_state =
150 GetVariableInput(context, node, kCellStateTensor);
151 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, cell_state != nullptr);
152 TfLiteTensor* output_tensor;
153 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
154 context, GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputTensor, &output_tensor));
155
156 auto* cell_state_params =
157 static_cast<TfLiteAffineQuantization*>(cell_state->quantization.params);
158 auto* proj_params = static_cast<TfLiteAffineQuantization*>(
159 output_tensor->quantization.params);
160 if (cell_clip > 0.0) {
161 integer_lstm_param->quantized_cell_clip = static_cast<int16_t>(std::min(
162 std::max(cell_clip / cell_state_params->scale->data[0], -32768.0f),
163 32767.0f));
164 } else {
165 integer_lstm_param->quantized_cell_clip = 0;
166 }
167 if (proj_clip > 0.0) {
168 integer_lstm_param->quantized_proj_clip = static_cast<int8_t>(std::min(
169 std::max(proj_clip / proj_params->scale->data[0], -128.0f), 127.0f));
170 } else {
171 integer_lstm_param->quantized_proj_clip = 0;
172 }
173
174 // Calculate effective scales.
175 OpData* op_data = static_cast<OpData*>(node->user_data);
176 const bool use_layer_norm = op_data->use_layer_norm;
177
178 const TfLiteTensor* input;
179 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputTensor, &input));
180
181 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights =
182 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputToInputWeightsTensor);
183 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_forget_weights;
184 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
185 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToForgetWeightsTensor,
186 &input_to_forget_weights));
187 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_cell_weights;
188 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
189 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToCellWeightsTensor,
190 &input_to_cell_weights));
191 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_output_weights;
192 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
193 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToOutputWeightsTensor,
194 &input_to_output_weights));
195
196 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_input_weights =
197 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kRecurrentToInputWeightsTensor);
198 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_forget_weights;
199 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
200 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToForgetWeightsTensor,
201 &recurrent_to_forget_weights));
202 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_cell_weights;
203 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
204 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToCellWeightsTensor,
205 &recurrent_to_cell_weights));
206 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_output_weights;
207 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
208 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToOutputWeightsTensor,
209 &recurrent_to_output_weights));
210
211 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_input_weights =
212 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToInputWeightsTensor);
213 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_forget_weights =
214 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToForgetWeightsTensor);
215 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_output_weights =
216 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToOutputWeightsTensor);
217
218 const TfLiteTensor* input_layer_norm_coefficients =
219 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
220 const TfLiteTensor* forget_layer_norm_coefficients =
221 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kForgetLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
222 const TfLiteTensor* cell_layer_norm_coefficients =
223 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
224 const TfLiteTensor* output_layer_norm_coefficients =
225 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kOutputLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
226
227 const TfLiteTensor* projection_weights =
228 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionWeightsTensor);
229
230 TfLiteTensor* output_state =
231 GetVariableInput(context, node, kOutputStateTensor);
232 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, output_state != nullptr);
233
234 // Since we have already checked that weights are all there or none, we can
235 // check the existence of only one to get the condition.
236 const bool use_cifg = (input_to_input_weights == nullptr);
237 const bool use_peephole = (cell_to_output_weights != nullptr);
238 const bool use_projection = (projection_weights != nullptr);
239
240 // Get intermediate scales and zero points.
241 std::vector<float> intermediate_scale;
242 std::vector<int32> intermediate_zp;
243 for (int i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
244 if (use_layer_norm) {
245 TfLiteTensor* intermediate;
246 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
247 GetIntermediatesSafe(context, node, i, &intermediate));
248 auto* params = static_cast<TfLiteAffineQuantization*>(
249 intermediate->quantization.params);
250 intermediate_scale.push_back(params->scale->data[0]);
251 intermediate_zp.push_back(params->zero_point->data[0]);
252 } else {
253 // Q3.12 for activation functions.
254 intermediate_scale.push_back(std::pow(2, -12));
255 intermediate_zp.push_back(0);
256 }
257 }
258 // In the absence of projection, hidden becomes output and this intermediate
259 // is ignored.
260 TfLiteTensor* hidden;
261 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetIntermediatesSafe(context, node, 4, &hidden));
262 auto* hidden_params =
263 static_cast<TfLiteAffineQuantization*>(hidden->quantization.params);
264 intermediate_scale.push_back(hidden_params->scale->data[0]);
265 intermediate_zp.push_back(hidden_params->zero_point->data[0]);
266
267 // Scales.
268 const float default_scale = 1.0;
269 float input_scale = default_scale;
270 float input_to_input_weight_scale = default_scale;
271 float recurrent_to_input_weight_scale = default_scale;
272 float cell_to_input_weight_scale = default_scale;
273 float input_to_forget_weight_scale = default_scale;
274 float recurrent_to_forget_weight_scale = default_scale;
275 float cell_to_forget_weight_scale = default_scale;
276 float input_to_cell_weight_scale = default_scale;
277 float recurrent_to_cell_weight_scale = default_scale;
278 float input_to_output_weight_scale = default_scale;
279 float recurrent_to_output_weight_scale = default_scale;
280 float cell_to_output_weight_scale = default_scale;
281 float projection_weight_scale = default_scale;
282 float layer_norm_input_scale = default_scale;
283 float layer_norm_forget_scale = default_scale;
284 float layer_norm_cell_scale = default_scale;
285 float layer_norm_output_scale = default_scale;
286 float output_state_scale = default_scale;
287 int cell_scale = 1;
288
289 // Effective scales.
290 float effective_input_to_input_scale = default_scale;
291 float effective_recurrent_to_input_scale = default_scale;
292 float effective_cell_to_input_scale = default_scale;
293 float effective_input_to_forget_scale = default_scale;
294 float effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale = default_scale;
295 float effective_cell_to_forget_scale = default_scale;
296 float effective_input_to_cell_scale = default_scale;
297 float effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale = default_scale;
298 float effective_input_to_output_scale = default_scale;
299 float effective_recurrent_to_output_scale = default_scale;
300 float effective_cell_to_output_scale = default_scale;
301 float effective_proj_scale = default_scale;
302 float effective_hidden_scale = default_scale;
303
304 // Populate scales.
305 if (!use_cifg) {
306 input_to_input_weight_scale = input_to_input_weights->params.scale;
307 recurrent_to_input_weight_scale = recurrent_to_input_weights->params.scale;
308 }
309
310 if (use_peephole) {
311 if (!use_cifg) {
312 cell_to_input_weight_scale = cell_to_input_weights->params.scale;
313 }
314 cell_to_forget_weight_scale = cell_to_forget_weights->params.scale;
315 cell_to_output_weight_scale = cell_to_output_weights->params.scale;
316 }
317
318 if (use_layer_norm) {
319 if (!use_cifg) {
320 layer_norm_input_scale = input_layer_norm_coefficients->params.scale;
321 }
322 layer_norm_forget_scale = forget_layer_norm_coefficients->params.scale;
323 layer_norm_cell_scale = cell_layer_norm_coefficients->params.scale;
324 layer_norm_output_scale = output_layer_norm_coefficients->params.scale;
325 }
326
327 if (use_projection) {
328 projection_weight_scale = projection_weights->params.scale;
329 }
330 output_state_scale = output_state->params.scale;
331
332 input_to_forget_weight_scale = input_to_forget_weights->params.scale;
333 input_to_cell_weight_scale = input_to_cell_weights->params.scale;
334 input_to_output_weight_scale = input_to_output_weights->params.scale;
335 recurrent_to_forget_weight_scale = recurrent_to_forget_weights->params.scale;
336 recurrent_to_cell_weight_scale = recurrent_to_cell_weights->params.scale;
337 recurrent_to_output_weight_scale = recurrent_to_output_weights->params.scale;
338
339 // Check cell state (already used above)
340 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, CheckedLog2(cell_state->params.scale, &cell_scale));
341 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, cell_scale <= -9);
342 integer_lstm_param->cell_scale = cell_scale;
343 input_scale = input->params.scale;
344
345 // Calculate effective scales.
346 if (!use_cifg) {
347 effective_input_to_input_scale =
348 input_to_input_weight_scale * input_scale / intermediate_scale[0];
349 effective_recurrent_to_input_scale = recurrent_to_input_weight_scale *
350 output_state_scale /
351 intermediate_scale[0];
352 }
353 effective_input_to_forget_scale =
354 input_to_forget_weight_scale * input_scale / intermediate_scale[1];
355 effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale = recurrent_to_forget_weight_scale *
356 output_state_scale /
357 intermediate_scale[1];
358
359 effective_input_to_cell_scale =
360 input_to_cell_weight_scale * input_scale / intermediate_scale[2];
361 effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale = recurrent_to_cell_weight_scale *
362 output_state_scale /
363 intermediate_scale[2];
364
365 effective_input_to_output_scale =
366 input_to_output_weight_scale * input_scale / intermediate_scale[3];
367 effective_recurrent_to_output_scale = recurrent_to_output_weight_scale *
368 output_state_scale /
369 intermediate_scale[3];
370
371 effective_hidden_scale =
372 std::pow(2, -15) / intermediate_scale[4] * std::pow(2, -15);
373
374 effective_proj_scale =
375 projection_weight_scale * intermediate_scale[4] / output_state_scale;
376
377 if (use_peephole) {
378 if (!use_cifg) {
379 effective_cell_to_input_scale = std::pow(2, cell_scale) * // NOLINT
380 cell_to_input_weight_scale /
381 intermediate_scale[0];
382 }
383 effective_cell_to_forget_scale = std::pow(2, cell_scale) * // NOLINT
384 cell_to_forget_weight_scale /
385 intermediate_scale[1];
386 effective_cell_to_output_scale = std::pow(2, cell_scale) * // NOLINT
387 cell_to_output_weight_scale /
388 intermediate_scale[3];
389 }
390
391 // Decompose scales.
392 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_input_to_input_scale,
393 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_input_scale_a,
394 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_input_scale_b);
395 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_recurrent_to_input_scale,
396 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_input_scale_a,
397 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_input_scale_b);
398 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_cell_to_input_scale,
399 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_input_scale_a,
400 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_input_scale_b);
401 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_input_to_forget_scale,
402 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_forget_scale_a,
403 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_forget_scale_b);
404 QuantizeMultiplier(
405 effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale,
406 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale_a,
407 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale_b);
408 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_cell_to_forget_scale,
409 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_forget_scale_a,
410 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_forget_scale_b);
411 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_input_to_cell_scale,
412 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_cell_scale_a,
413 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_cell_scale_b);
414 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale,
415 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale_a,
416 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale_b);
417 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_input_to_output_scale,
418 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_output_scale_a,
419 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_output_scale_b);
420 QuantizeMultiplier(
421 effective_recurrent_to_output_scale,
422 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_output_scale_a,
423 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_output_scale_b);
424 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_cell_to_output_scale,
425 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_output_scale_a,
426 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_output_scale_b);
427 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_proj_scale,
428 &integer_lstm_param->effective_proj_scale_a,
429 &integer_lstm_param->effective_proj_scale_b);
430 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_hidden_scale,
431 &integer_lstm_param->effective_hidden_scale_a,
432 &integer_lstm_param->effective_hidden_scale_b);
433 QuantizeMultiplier(layer_norm_input_scale,
434 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_input_scale_a,
435 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_input_scale_b);
436 QuantizeMultiplier(layer_norm_forget_scale,
437 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_forget_scale_a,
438 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_forget_scale_b);
439 QuantizeMultiplier(layer_norm_cell_scale,
440 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_cell_scale_a,
441 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_cell_scale_b);
442 QuantizeMultiplier(layer_norm_output_scale,
443 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_output_scale_a,
444 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_output_scale_b);
445
446 integer_lstm_param->hidden_zp = intermediate_zp[4];
447
448 // 10000 is used to make sure the kernel logic does not overflow.
449 if (!use_cifg) {
450 integer_lstm_param->input_variance_guard =
451 std::max(1, static_cast<int32_t>(10000 * layer_norm_input_scale));
452 }
453 integer_lstm_param->forget_variance_guard =
454 std::max(1, static_cast<int32_t>(10000 * layer_norm_forget_scale));
455 integer_lstm_param->cell_variance_guard =
456 std::max(1, static_cast<int32_t>(10000 * layer_norm_cell_scale));
457 integer_lstm_param->output_variance_guard =
458 std::max(1, static_cast<int32_t>(10000 * layer_norm_output_scale));
459
460 return kTfLiteOk;
461}
462
463TfLiteStatus PopulateQuantizedLstmParams8x8_8(
464 TfLiteContext* context, TfLiteNode* node,
465 lstm_eval::IntegerLstmParameter* integer_lstm_param) {
466 // Get all tensors.
467 const TfLiteTensor* input;
468 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputTensor, &input));
469 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights =
470 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputToInputWeightsTensor);
471 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_forget_weights;
472 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
473 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToForgetWeightsTensor,
474 &input_to_forget_weights));
475 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_cell_weights;
476 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
477 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToCellWeightsTensor,
478 &input_to_cell_weights));
479 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_output_weights;
480 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
481 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToOutputWeightsTensor,
482 &input_to_output_weights));
483
484 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_input_weights =
485 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kRecurrentToInputWeightsTensor);
486 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_forget_weights;
487 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
488 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToForgetWeightsTensor,
489 &recurrent_to_forget_weights));
490 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_cell_weights;
491 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
492 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToCellWeightsTensor,
493 &recurrent_to_cell_weights));
494 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_output_weights;
495 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
496 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToOutputWeightsTensor,
497 &recurrent_to_output_weights));
498
499 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_input_weights =
500 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToInputWeightsTensor);
501 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_forget_weights =
502 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToForgetWeightsTensor);
503 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_output_weights =
504 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToOutputWeightsTensor);
505
506 const TfLiteTensor* input_layer_norm_coefficients =
507 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
508 const TfLiteTensor* forget_layer_norm_coefficients =
509 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kForgetLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
510 const TfLiteTensor* cell_layer_norm_coefficients =
511 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
512 const TfLiteTensor* output_layer_norm_coefficients =
513 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kOutputLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
514
515 const TfLiteTensor* input_gate_bias =
516 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputGateBiasTensor);
517 const TfLiteTensor* forget_gate_bias;
518 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kForgetGateBiasTensor,
519 &forget_gate_bias));
520 const TfLiteTensor* cell_gate_bias;
521 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kCellGateBiasTensor,
522 &cell_gate_bias));
523 const TfLiteTensor* output_gate_bias;
524 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kOutputGateBiasTensor,
525 &output_gate_bias));
526
527 const TfLiteTensor* projection_weights =
528 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionWeightsTensor);
529 const TfLiteTensor* projection_bias =
530 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionBiasTensor);
531
532 TfLiteTensor* output_state =
533 GetVariableInput(context, node, kOutputStateTensor);
534 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, output_state != nullptr);
535 TfLiteTensor* cell_state = GetVariableInput(context, node, kCellStateTensor);
536 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, cell_state != nullptr);
537
538 // Since we have already checked that weights are all there or none, we can
539 // check the existence of only one to get the condition.
540 const bool use_cifg = (input_to_input_weights == nullptr);
541 const bool use_peephole = (cell_to_output_weights != nullptr);
542 const bool is_layer_norm_lstm = (forget_layer_norm_coefficients != nullptr);
543 const bool use_projection = (projection_weights != nullptr);
544
545 // Weights and states.
546 int8_t* input_to_input_weight_ptr = nullptr;
547 int8_t* recurrent_to_input_weight_ptr = nullptr;
548 int8_t* cell_to_input_weight_ptr = nullptr;
549 int8_t* input_to_forget_weight_ptr = nullptr;
550 int8_t* recurrent_to_forget_weight_ptr = nullptr;
551 int8_t* cell_to_forget_weight_ptr = nullptr;
552 int8_t* input_to_cell_weight_ptr = nullptr;
553 int8_t* recurrent_to_cell_weight_ptr = nullptr;
554 int8_t* input_to_output_weight_ptr = nullptr;
555 int8_t* recurrent_to_output_weight_ptr = nullptr;
556 int8_t* cell_to_output_weight_ptr = nullptr;
557 int8_t* projection_weight_ptr = nullptr;
558 int16_t* layer_norm_input_weight_ptr = nullptr;
559 int16_t* layer_norm_forget_weight_ptr = nullptr;
560 int16_t* layer_norm_cell_weight_ptr = nullptr;
561 int16_t* layer_norm_output_weight_ptr = nullptr;
562 int32_t* input_gate_bias_ptr = nullptr;
563 int32_t* forget_gate_bias_ptr = nullptr;
564 int32_t* cell_gate_bias_ptr = nullptr;
565 int32_t* output_gate_bias_ptr = nullptr;
566 int32_t* projection_bias_ptr = nullptr;
567 int16_t* cell_ptr = nullptr;
568 int8_t* output_state_ptr = nullptr;
569
570 // Scales.
571 const float default_scale = 1.0;
572 float input_scale = default_scale;
573 float input_to_input_weight_scale = default_scale;
574 float recurrent_to_input_weight_scale = default_scale;
575 float cell_to_input_weight_scale = default_scale;
576 float input_to_forget_weight_scale = default_scale;
577 float recurrent_to_forget_weight_scale = default_scale;
578 float cell_to_forget_weight_scale = default_scale;
579 float input_to_cell_weight_scale = default_scale;
580 float recurrent_to_cell_weight_scale = default_scale;
581 float input_to_output_weight_scale = default_scale;
582 float recurrent_to_output_weight_scale = default_scale;
583 float cell_to_output_weight_scale = default_scale;
584 float projection_weight_scale = default_scale;
585 float layer_norm_input_scale = default_scale;
586 float layer_norm_forget_scale = default_scale;
587 float layer_norm_cell_scale = default_scale;
588 float layer_norm_output_scale = default_scale;
589 float output_state_scale = default_scale;
590
591 // Effective scales.
592 float effective_input_to_input_scale = default_scale;
593 float effective_recurrent_to_input_scale = default_scale;
594 float effective_cell_to_input_scale = default_scale;
595 float effective_input_to_forget_scale = default_scale;
596 float effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale = default_scale;
597 float effective_cell_to_forget_scale = default_scale;
598 float effective_input_to_cell_scale = default_scale;
599 float effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale = default_scale;
600 float effective_input_to_output_scale = default_scale;
601 float effective_recurrent_to_output_scale = default_scale;
602 float effective_cell_to_output_scale = default_scale;
603 float effective_proj_scale = default_scale;
604
605 // Zero points
606 int input_zp = 0;
607 int output_state_zp = 0;
608
609 // Populate all the values.
610 if (!use_cifg) {
611 input_to_input_weight_ptr = input_to_input_weights->data.int8;
612 recurrent_to_input_weight_ptr = recurrent_to_input_weights->data.int8;
613 input_gate_bias_ptr = input_gate_bias->data.i32;
614 input_to_input_weight_scale = input_to_input_weights->params.scale;
615 recurrent_to_input_weight_scale = recurrent_to_input_weights->params.scale;
616 }
617
618 if (use_peephole) {
619 if (!use_cifg) {
620 cell_to_input_weight_ptr = cell_to_input_weights->data.int8;
621 cell_to_input_weight_scale = cell_to_input_weights->params.scale;
622 }
623 cell_to_forget_weight_ptr = cell_to_forget_weights->data.int8;
624 cell_to_output_weight_ptr = cell_to_output_weights->data.int8;
625 cell_to_forget_weight_scale = cell_to_forget_weights->params.scale;
626 cell_to_output_weight_scale = cell_to_output_weights->params.scale;
627 }
628
629 if (is_layer_norm_lstm) {
630 if (!use_cifg) {
631 layer_norm_input_weight_ptr = input_layer_norm_coefficients->data.i16;
632 layer_norm_input_scale = input_layer_norm_coefficients->params.scale;
633 }
634 layer_norm_forget_weight_ptr = forget_layer_norm_coefficients->data.i16;
635 layer_norm_forget_scale = forget_layer_norm_coefficients->params.scale;
636 layer_norm_cell_weight_ptr = cell_layer_norm_coefficients->data.i16;
637 layer_norm_cell_scale = cell_layer_norm_coefficients->params.scale;
638 layer_norm_output_weight_ptr = output_layer_norm_coefficients->data.i16;
639 layer_norm_output_scale = output_layer_norm_coefficients->params.scale;
640 }
641
642 if (use_projection) {
643 projection_weight_ptr = projection_weights->data.int8;
644 projection_weight_scale = projection_weights->params.scale;
645 if (projection_bias) {
646 projection_bias_ptr = projection_bias->data.i32;
647 }
648 }
649 output_state_scale = output_state->params.scale;
650
651 input_to_forget_weight_ptr = input_to_forget_weights->data.int8;
652 input_to_forget_weight_scale = input_to_forget_weights->params.scale;
653 input_to_cell_weight_ptr = input_to_cell_weights->data.int8;
654 input_to_cell_weight_scale = input_to_cell_weights->params.scale;
655 input_to_output_weight_ptr = input_to_output_weights->data.int8;
656 input_to_output_weight_scale = input_to_output_weights->params.scale;
657 recurrent_to_forget_weight_ptr = recurrent_to_forget_weights->data.int8;
658 recurrent_to_forget_weight_scale = recurrent_to_forget_weights->params.scale;
659 recurrent_to_cell_weight_ptr = recurrent_to_cell_weights->data.int8;
660 recurrent_to_cell_weight_scale = recurrent_to_cell_weights->params.scale;
661 recurrent_to_output_weight_ptr = recurrent_to_output_weights->data.int8;
662 recurrent_to_output_weight_scale = recurrent_to_output_weights->params.scale;
663 forget_gate_bias_ptr = forget_gate_bias->data.i32;
664 cell_gate_bias_ptr = cell_gate_bias->data.i32;
665 output_gate_bias_ptr = output_gate_bias->data.i32;
666 output_state_ptr = output_state->data.int8;
667 cell_ptr = cell_state->data.i16;
668 input_scale = input->params.scale;
669 input_zp = input->params.zero_point;
670 output_state_zp = output_state->params.zero_point;
671
672 std::vector<float> intermediate_scale;
673 for (int i = 0; i < 12; ++i) {
674 TfLiteTensor* intermediate =
675 &context->tensors[node->intermediates->data[i]];
676 auto* params = reinterpret_cast<TfLiteAffineQuantization*>(
677 intermediate->quantization.params);
678 intermediate_scale.push_back(params->scale->data[0]);
679 integer_lstm_param->intermediate_zp[i] = params->zero_point->data[0];
680 }
681
682 // Calculate effective scales.
683 if (!use_cifg) {
684 effective_input_to_input_scale =
685 input_to_input_weight_scale * input_scale / intermediate_scale[1];
686 effective_recurrent_to_input_scale = recurrent_to_input_weight_scale *
687 output_state_scale /
688 intermediate_scale[2];
689 }
690 effective_input_to_forget_scale =
691 input_to_forget_weight_scale * input_scale / intermediate_scale[4];
692 effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale = recurrent_to_forget_weight_scale *
693 output_state_scale /
694 intermediate_scale[5];
695
696 effective_input_to_cell_scale =
697 input_to_cell_weight_scale * input_scale / intermediate_scale[7];
698 effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale = recurrent_to_cell_weight_scale *
699 output_state_scale /
700 intermediate_scale[8];
701
702 effective_input_to_output_scale =
703 input_to_output_weight_scale * input_scale / intermediate_scale[10];
704 effective_recurrent_to_output_scale = recurrent_to_output_weight_scale *
705 output_state_scale /
706 intermediate_scale[11];
707 effective_proj_scale =
708 projection_weight_scale * std::pow(2, -15) / output_state_scale;
709
710 if (use_peephole) {
711 if (!use_cifg) {
712 effective_cell_to_input_scale =
713 std::pow(2, -15) * cell_to_input_weight_scale / intermediate_scale[0];
714 }
715 effective_cell_to_forget_scale =
716 std::pow(2, -15) * cell_to_forget_weight_scale / intermediate_scale[3];
717 effective_cell_to_output_scale =
718 std::pow(2, -15) * cell_to_output_weight_scale / intermediate_scale[9];
719 }
720
721 // Calculate effecgive scales.
722 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_input_to_input_scale,
723 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_input_scale_a,
724 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_input_scale_b);
725 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_recurrent_to_input_scale,
726 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_input_scale_a,
727 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_input_scale_b);
728 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_cell_to_input_scale,
729 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_input_scale_a,
730 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_input_scale_b);
731 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_input_to_forget_scale,
732 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_forget_scale_a,
733 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_forget_scale_b);
734 QuantizeMultiplier(
735 effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale,
736 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale_a,
737 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_forget_scale_b);
738 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_cell_to_forget_scale,
739 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_forget_scale_a,
740 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_forget_scale_b);
741 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_input_to_cell_scale,
742 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_cell_scale_a,
743 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_cell_scale_b);
744 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale,
745 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale_a,
746 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_cell_scale_b);
747 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_input_to_output_scale,
748 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_output_scale_a,
749 &integer_lstm_param->effective_input_to_output_scale_b);
750 QuantizeMultiplier(
751 effective_recurrent_to_output_scale,
752 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_output_scale_a,
753 &integer_lstm_param->effective_recurrent_to_output_scale_b);
754 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_cell_to_output_scale,
755 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_output_scale_a,
756 &integer_lstm_param->effective_cell_to_output_scale_b);
757 QuantizeMultiplier(effective_proj_scale,
758 &integer_lstm_param->effective_proj_scale_a,
759 &integer_lstm_param->effective_proj_scale_b);
760 QuantizeMultiplier(layer_norm_input_scale,
761 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_input_scale_a,
762 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_input_scale_b);
763 QuantizeMultiplier(layer_norm_forget_scale,
764 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_forget_scale_a,
765 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_forget_scale_b);
766 QuantizeMultiplier(layer_norm_cell_scale,
767 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_cell_scale_a,
768 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_cell_scale_b);
769 QuantizeMultiplier(layer_norm_output_scale,
770 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_output_scale_a,
771 &integer_lstm_param->layer_norm_output_scale_b);
772
773 {
774 // Intermdiates in flatbuffer holds Wx, Wh and Wx+Wh.
775 // effective Wx, Wh is in effective_input/recurrent_to_<...>_scale
776 // So use intermediate_scale to hold scale from Wx and Wh to Wx+Wh
777 // 0: [1] -> [0]
778 // 1: [2] -> [0]
779 // and use intermdiate_zp as is.
780 const float s_1_0 = intermediate_scale[1] / intermediate_scale[0];
781 const float s_2_0 = intermediate_scale[2] / intermediate_scale[0];
782 const float s_4_3 = intermediate_scale[4] / intermediate_scale[3];
783 const float s_5_3 = intermediate_scale[5] / intermediate_scale[3];
784 const float s_7_6 = intermediate_scale[7] / intermediate_scale[6];
785 const float s_8_6 = intermediate_scale[8] / intermediate_scale[6];
786 const float s_10_9 = intermediate_scale[10] / intermediate_scale[9];
787 const float s_11_9 = intermediate_scale[11] / intermediate_scale[9];
788 QuantizeMultiplier(s_1_0, &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_a[0],
789 &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_b[0]);
790 QuantizeMultiplier(s_2_0, &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_a[1],
791 &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_b[1]);
792 QuantizeMultiplier(s_4_3, &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_a[2],
793 &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_b[2]);
794 QuantizeMultiplier(s_5_3, &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_a[3],
795 &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_b[3]);
796 QuantizeMultiplier(s_7_6, &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_a[4],
797 &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_b[4]);
798 QuantizeMultiplier(s_8_6, &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_a[5],
799 &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_b[5]);
800 QuantizeMultiplier(s_10_9, &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_a[6],
801 &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_b[6]);
802 QuantizeMultiplier(s_11_9, &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_a[7],
803 &integer_lstm_param->intermediate_scale_b[7]);
804 }
805
806 // Calculate quantized clip for projection and cell.
807 const auto* params = reinterpret_cast<TfLiteLSTMParams*>(node->builtin_data);
808 const float cell_clip = params->cell_clip;
809 const float proj_clip = params->proj_clip;
810
811 TfLiteTensor* output_tensor;
812 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
813 context, GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputTensor, &output_tensor));
814
815 auto* cell_state_params = reinterpret_cast<TfLiteAffineQuantization*>(
816 cell_state->quantization.params);
817 auto* proj_params = reinterpret_cast<TfLiteAffineQuantization*>(
818 output_tensor->quantization.params);
819 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_state_params->scale->data[0], 1.0 / 32768);
820 if (cell_clip > 0.0 && cell_clip < 1.0) {
821 integer_lstm_param->quantized_cell_clip = static_cast<int16_t>(std::min(
822 std::max(cell_clip / cell_state_params->scale->data[0], -32768.0f),
823 32767.0f));
824 } else {
825 integer_lstm_param->quantized_cell_clip = 0;
826 }
827 if (proj_clip > 0.0) {
828 integer_lstm_param->quantized_proj_clip = static_cast<int8_t>(std::min(
829 std::max(proj_clip / proj_params->scale->data[0], -128.0f), 127.0f));
830 } else {
831 integer_lstm_param->quantized_proj_clip = 0;
832 }
833 return kTfLiteOk;
834}
835
836} // namespace
837
838void* Init(TfLiteContext* context, const char* buffer, size_t length) {
839 auto* op_data = new OpData();
840 op_data->kernel_type = kTfLiteLSTMFullKernel;
841 // TODO(b/159066113): maybe just add the minimum required temp tensors?
842 context->AddTensors(context, kNumHybridTemporaryTensors,
843 &op_data->scratch_tensor_index);
844 // Tensors used for the sparse hybrid kernel.
845 context->AddTensors(context, /*tensors_to_add=*/kLedgersToAdd,
846 &op_data->ledger_index);
847 return op_data;
848}
849
850// LINT.IfChange
851// Check that input tensor dimensions matches with each other.
852TfLiteStatus CheckInputTensorDimensions(TfLiteContext* context,
853 TfLiteNode* node, int n_input,
854 int n_output, int n_cell,
855 bool use_layer_norm, bool is_integer) {
856 const auto* params = static_cast<TfLiteLSTMParams*>(node->builtin_data);
857
858 // Making sure clipping parameters have valid values.
859 // == 0 means no clipping
860 // > 0 means clipping
861 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, params->cell_clip >= 0);
862 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, params->proj_clip >= 0);
863
864 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_forget_weights;
865 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
866 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToForgetWeightsTensor,
867 &input_to_forget_weights));
868 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_forget_weights->dims->size, 2);
869 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_forget_weights->dims->data[0], n_cell);
870 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_forget_weights->dims->data[1], n_input);
871 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, (input_to_forget_weights->type == kTfLiteFloat32) ||
872 (input_to_forget_weights->type == kTfLiteUInt8) ||
873 (input_to_forget_weights->type == kTfLiteInt8));
874
875 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights =
876 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputToInputWeightsTensor);
877 const bool use_cifg = (input_to_input_weights == nullptr);
878 if (!use_cifg) {
879 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_input_weights->dims->size, 2);
880 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_input_weights->dims->data[0], n_cell);
881 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_input_weights->dims->data[1], n_input);
882 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, input_to_input_weights->type,
883 input_to_forget_weights->type);
884 }
885
886 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_cell_weights;
887 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
888 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToCellWeightsTensor,
889 &input_to_cell_weights));
890 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_cell_weights->dims->size, 2);
891 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_cell_weights->dims->data[0], n_cell);
892 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_cell_weights->dims->data[1], n_input);
893 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, input_to_cell_weights->type,
894 input_to_forget_weights->type);
895
896 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_input_weights =
897 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kRecurrentToInputWeightsTensor);
898 if (recurrent_to_input_weights != nullptr) {
899 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_input_weights->dims->size, 2);
900 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_input_weights->dims->data[0],
901 n_cell);
902 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_input_weights->dims->data[1],
903 n_output);
904 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, recurrent_to_input_weights->type,
905 input_to_forget_weights->type);
906 }
907
908 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_forget_weights;
909 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
910 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToForgetWeightsTensor,
911 &recurrent_to_forget_weights));
912 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_forget_weights->dims->size, 2);
913 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_forget_weights->dims->data[0],
914 n_cell);
915 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_forget_weights->dims->data[1],
916 n_output);
917 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, recurrent_to_forget_weights->type,
918 input_to_forget_weights->type);
919
920 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_cell_weights;
921 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
922 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToCellWeightsTensor,
923 &recurrent_to_cell_weights));
924 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_cell_weights->dims->size, 2);
925 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_cell_weights->dims->data[0], n_cell);
926 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_cell_weights->dims->data[1],
927 n_output);
928 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, recurrent_to_cell_weights->type,
929 input_to_forget_weights->type);
930
931 // We make sure the input-gate's parameters are either both present (regular
932 // LSTM) or not at all (CIFG-LSTM).
933 const bool cifg_weights_all_or_none =
934 ((input_to_input_weights != nullptr) &&
935 (recurrent_to_input_weights != nullptr)) ||
936 ((input_to_input_weights == nullptr) &&
937 (recurrent_to_input_weights == nullptr));
938 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, cifg_weights_all_or_none == true);
939
940 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_input_weights =
941 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToInputWeightsTensor);
942 if (cell_to_input_weights) {
943 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_to_input_weights->dims->size, 1);
944 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_to_input_weights->dims->data[0], n_cell);
945 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(
946 context, cell_to_input_weights->type,
947 is_integer ? kTfLiteInt16 : input_to_forget_weights->type);
948 }
949
950 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_forget_weights =
951 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToForgetWeightsTensor);
952 if (cell_to_forget_weights) {
953 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_to_forget_weights->dims->size, 1);
954 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_to_forget_weights->dims->data[0], n_cell);
955 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(
956 context, cell_to_forget_weights->type,
957 is_integer ? kTfLiteInt16 : input_to_forget_weights->type);
958 }
959
960 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_output_weights =
961 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToOutputWeightsTensor);
962 if (cell_to_output_weights) {
963 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_to_output_weights->dims->size, 1);
964 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_to_output_weights->dims->data[0], n_cell);
965 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(
966 context, cell_to_output_weights->type,
967 is_integer ? kTfLiteInt16 : input_to_forget_weights->type);
968 }
969
970 // Making sure the peephole weights are there all or none.
971 const bool peephole_weights_all_or_none =
972 ((cell_to_input_weights != nullptr || use_cifg) &&
973 (cell_to_forget_weights != nullptr) &&
974 (cell_to_output_weights != nullptr)) ||
975 ((cell_to_input_weights == nullptr) &&
976 (cell_to_forget_weights == nullptr) &&
977 (cell_to_output_weights == nullptr));
978 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, peephole_weights_all_or_none == true);
979
980 // Make sure the input gate bias is present only when not a CIFG-LSTM.
981 const TfLiteTensor* input_gate_bias =
982 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputGateBiasTensor);
983 if (use_cifg) {
984 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_gate_bias, nullptr);
985 } else {
986 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_gate_bias->dims->size, 1);
987 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_gate_bias->dims->data[0], n_cell);
988 if (is_integer) {
989 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, input_gate_bias->type, kTfLiteInt32);
990 } else {
991 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, input_gate_bias->type, kTfLiteFloat32);
992 }
993 }
994
995 const TfLiteTensor* forget_gate_bias;
996 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kForgetGateBiasTensor,
997 &forget_gate_bias));
998 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, forget_gate_bias->dims->size, 1);
999 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, forget_gate_bias->dims->data[0], n_cell);
1000 if (is_integer) {
1001 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, forget_gate_bias->type, kTfLiteInt32);
1002 } else {
1003 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, forget_gate_bias->type, kTfLiteFloat32);
1004 }
1005
1006 const TfLiteTensor* cell_gate_bias;
1007 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kCellGateBiasTensor,
1008 &cell_gate_bias));
1009 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_gate_bias->dims->size, 1);
1010 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_gate_bias->dims->data[0], n_cell);
1011 if (is_integer) {
1012 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, cell_gate_bias->type, kTfLiteInt32);
1013 } else {
1014 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, cell_gate_bias->type, kTfLiteFloat32);
1015 }
1016
1017 const TfLiteTensor* output_gate_bias;
1018 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kOutputGateBiasTensor,
1019 &output_gate_bias));
1020 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, output_gate_bias->dims->size, 1);
1021 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, output_gate_bias->dims->data[0], n_cell);
1022 if (is_integer) {
1023 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, output_gate_bias->type, kTfLiteInt32);
1024 } else {
1025 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, output_gate_bias->type, kTfLiteFloat32);
1026 }
1027
1028 const TfLiteTensor* projection_weights =
1029 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionWeightsTensor);
1030 if (projection_weights != nullptr) {
1031 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, projection_weights->dims->size, 2);
1032 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, projection_weights->dims->data[0], n_output);
1033 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, projection_weights->dims->data[1], n_cell);
1034 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, projection_weights->type,
1035 input_to_forget_weights->type);
1036 }
1037
1038 const TfLiteTensor* projection_bias =
1039 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionBiasTensor);
1040 if (projection_bias != nullptr) {
1041 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, projection_bias->dims->size, 1);
1042 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, projection_bias->dims->data[0], n_output);
1043 if (is_integer) {
1044 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, projection_bias->type, kTfLiteInt32);
1045 } else {
1046 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, projection_bias->type, kTfLiteFloat32);
1047 }
1048 }
1049
1050 // Making sure the projection tensors are consistent:
1051 // 1) If projection weight is not present, then projection bias should not be
1052 // present.
1053 // 2) If projection weight is present, then projection bias is optional.
1054 // TODO(ghodrat): make sure this is correct.
1055 const bool projection_tensors_consistent =
1056 ((projection_weights != nullptr) || (projection_bias == nullptr));
1057 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, projection_tensors_consistent == true);
1058
1059 if (use_layer_norm) {
1060 const TfLiteTensor* input_layer_norm_coefficients = GetOptionalInputTensor(
1061 context, node, kInputLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1062 if (use_cifg) {
1063 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_layer_norm_coefficients, nullptr);
1064 } else {
1065 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, input_layer_norm_coefficients != nullptr);
1066 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_layer_norm_coefficients->dims->size, 1);
1067 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_layer_norm_coefficients->dims->data[0],
1068 n_cell);
1069 if (is_integer) {
1070 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, input_layer_norm_coefficients->type,
1071 kTfLiteInt16);
1072 } else {
1073 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, input_layer_norm_coefficients->type,
1074 kTfLiteFloat32);
1075 }
1076 }
1077
1078 const TfLiteTensor* forget_layer_norm_coefficients = GetOptionalInputTensor(
1079 context, node, kForgetLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1080 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, forget_layer_norm_coefficients != nullptr);
1081 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, forget_layer_norm_coefficients->dims->size, 1);
1082 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, forget_layer_norm_coefficients->dims->data[0],
1083 n_cell);
1084 if (is_integer) {
1085 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, forget_layer_norm_coefficients->type,
1086 kTfLiteInt16);
1087 } else {
1088 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, forget_layer_norm_coefficients->type,
1089 kTfLiteFloat32);
1090 }
1091
1092 const TfLiteTensor* cell_layer_norm_coefficients =
1093 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1094 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, cell_layer_norm_coefficients != nullptr);
1095 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_layer_norm_coefficients->dims->size, 1);
1096 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, cell_layer_norm_coefficients->dims->data[0],
1097 n_cell);
1098 if (is_integer) {
1099 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, cell_layer_norm_coefficients->type,
1100 kTfLiteInt16);
1101 } else {
1102 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, cell_layer_norm_coefficients->type,
1103 kTfLiteFloat32);
1104 }
1105
1106 const TfLiteTensor* output_layer_norm_coefficients = GetOptionalInputTensor(
1107 context, node, kOutputLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1108 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, output_layer_norm_coefficients != nullptr);
1109 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, output_layer_norm_coefficients->dims->size, 1);
1110 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, output_layer_norm_coefficients->dims->data[0],
1111 n_cell);
1112 if (is_integer) {
1113 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, output_layer_norm_coefficients->type,
1114 kTfLiteInt16);
1115 } else {
1116 TF_LITE_ENSURE_TYPES_EQ(context, output_layer_norm_coefficients->type,
1117 kTfLiteFloat32);
1118 }
1119 }
1120
1121 return kTfLiteOk;
1122}
1123// LINT.ThenChange(//tensorflow/lite/tools/optimize/calibration/builtin_logging_ops/lstm.cc)
1124
1125TfLiteStatus PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1126 TfLiteContext* context, int32_t zero_point,
1127 const TfLiteTensor* weight_tensor, const TfLiteTensor* bias_tensor,
1128 std::unique_ptr<int32_t[]>* output) {
1129 if (weight_tensor == nullptr) {
1130 return kTfLiteOk;
1131 }
1132
1133 const RuntimeShape& weight_shape = GetTensorShape(weight_tensor);
1134 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, weight_shape.DimensionsCount(), 2);
1135 const int row = weight_shape.Dims(0);
1136 const int col = weight_shape.Dims(1);
1137 output->reset(new int32_t[row]);
1138 if (bias_tensor == nullptr) {
1139 memset(output->get(), 0, row * sizeof(int32_t));
1140 } else {
1141 const int32_t* bias = GetTensorData<int32_t>(bias_tensor);
1142 memcpy(output->get(), bias, row * sizeof(int32_t));
1143 }
1144 if (zero_point != 0) {
1145 const int8_t* weight = GetTensorData<int8_t>(weight_tensor);
1146 tensor_utils::MatrixScalarMultiplyAccumulate(weight, zero_point, row, col,
1147 output->get());
1148 }
1149 return kTfLiteOk;
1150}
1151
1152TfLiteStatus PopulatePrecomputedZPTimesWeightsWithBias(TfLiteContext* context,
1153 OpData* op_data,
1154 TfLiteNode* node) {
1155 const TfLiteTensor* input;
1156 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputTensor, &input));
1157 const TfLiteTensor* output_state =
1158 GetVariableInput(context, node, kOutputStateTensor);
1159 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, output_state != nullptr);
1160
1161 const int32_t input_zero_point = -input->params.zero_point;
1162 const int32_t output_state_zero_point = -output_state->params.zero_point;
1163
1164 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights =
1165 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputToInputWeightsTensor);
1166 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_forget_weights;
1167 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1168 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToForgetWeightsTensor,
1169 &input_to_forget_weights));
1170 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_cell_weights;
1171 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1172 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToCellWeightsTensor,
1173 &input_to_cell_weights));
1174 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_output_weights;
1175 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1176 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToOutputWeightsTensor,
1177 &input_to_output_weights));
1178
1179 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_input_weights =
1180 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kRecurrentToInputWeightsTensor);
1181 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_forget_weights;
1182 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1183 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToForgetWeightsTensor,
1184 &recurrent_to_forget_weights));
1185 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_cell_weights;
1186 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1187 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToCellWeightsTensor,
1188 &recurrent_to_cell_weights));
1189 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_output_weights;
1190 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1191 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToOutputWeightsTensor,
1192 &recurrent_to_output_weights));
1193
1194 const TfLiteTensor* projection_weights =
1195 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionWeightsTensor);
1196 const TfLiteTensor* projection_bias =
1197 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionBiasTensor);
1198
1199 lstm_eval::IntegerLstmParameter* integer_lstm_params =
1200 &op_data->integer_lstm_param;
1201
1202 const TfLiteTensor* intermediate =
1203 &context->tensors[node->intermediates->data[4]];
1204 const auto* params =
1205 static_cast<TfLiteAffineQuantization*>(intermediate->quantization.params);
1206 const int32_t hidden_zp = params->zero_point->data[0];
1207
1208 // Get bias and perform zero point calculation.
1209 // When there is layer normalization, the gate bias does not apply to matmul
1210 // directly:
1211 // y = ln(w * x + w * r + w * c) + b.
1212 const bool is_layer_norm = op_data->use_layer_norm;
1213
1214 // Forget gate.
1215 const TfLiteTensor* forget_gate_bias =
1216 is_layer_norm ? nullptr : GetInput(context, node, kForgetGateBiasTensor);
1217 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1218 context,
1219 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1220 context, input_zero_point, input_to_forget_weights, forget_gate_bias,
1221 &(integer_lstm_params->input_to_forget_effective_bias)));
1222
1223 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1224 context,
1225 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1226 context, output_state_zero_point, recurrent_to_forget_weights,
1227 nullptr, &(integer_lstm_params->recurrent_to_forget_effective_bias)));
1228
1229 // Modulation gate.
1230 const TfLiteTensor* cell_gate_bias =
1231 is_layer_norm ? nullptr : GetInput(context, node, kCellGateBiasTensor);
1232 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1233 context,
1234 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1235 context, input_zero_point, input_to_cell_weights, cell_gate_bias,
1236 &(integer_lstm_params->input_to_cell_effective_bias)));
1237 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1238 context,
1239 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1240 context, output_state_zero_point, recurrent_to_cell_weights, nullptr,
1241 &(integer_lstm_params->recurrent_to_cell_effective_bias)));
1242
1243 // Output gate.
1244 const TfLiteTensor* output_gate_bias =
1245 is_layer_norm ? nullptr : GetInput(context, node, kOutputGateBiasTensor);
1246 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1247 context,
1248 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1249 context, input_zero_point, input_to_output_weights, output_gate_bias,
1250 &(integer_lstm_params->input_to_output_effective_bias)));
1251
1252 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1253 context,
1254 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1255 context, output_state_zero_point, recurrent_to_output_weights,
1256 nullptr, &(integer_lstm_params->recurrent_to_output_effective_bias)));
1257
1258 // Input gate. The calculation is only meaningful for non-cifg case.
1259 const TfLiteTensor* input_gate_bias =
1260 is_layer_norm ? nullptr : GetInput(context, node, kInputGateBiasTensor);
1261 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1262 context,
1263 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1264 context, input_zero_point, input_to_input_weights, input_gate_bias,
1265 &(integer_lstm_params->input_to_input_effective_bias)));
1266 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1267 context,
1268 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1269 context, output_state_zero_point, recurrent_to_input_weights, nullptr,
1270 &(integer_lstm_params->recurrent_to_input_effective_bias)));
1271
1272 // Projection bias. The calculation is only meaningful for with projection.
1273 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1274 PrecomputeZeroPointTimesWeightWithBias(
1275 context, hidden_zp, projection_weights, projection_bias,
1276 &(integer_lstm_params->projection_effective_bias)));
1277 return kTfLiteOk;
1278}
1279
1280// Resize the output, state tensors based on the sizes of the input tensors.
1281// Allocate a temporary scratch tensor. Also check that the sizes of the input
1282// tensors match each other.
1283// LINT.IfChange
1284TfLiteStatus Prepare(TfLiteContext* context, TfLiteNode* node) {
1285 OpData* op_data = static_cast<OpData*>(node->user_data);
1286
1287 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, node->outputs->size, 1);
1288 // Logic for determining regular lstm and layer norm lstm:
1289 // input_size, forget_gate_layer_norm_tensor (20) null? is_layer_norm?
1290 // 20, N/A, No.
1291 // 24, null, No.
1292 // 24, not null, Yes.
1293 // 20-inputs lstm are deprecated and is only kept here for backward
1294 // compatibility.
1295 if (node->inputs->size == 24) {
1296 const TfLiteTensor* forget_layer_norm_coefficients = GetOptionalInputTensor(
1297 context, node, kForgetLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1298 if (forget_layer_norm_coefficients == nullptr) {
1299 op_data->use_layer_norm = false;
1300 } else {
1301 op_data->use_layer_norm = true;
1302 }
1303 } else if (node->inputs->size == 20) {
1304 // This is deprecated and is only kept here for backward compatibility.
1305 op_data->use_layer_norm = false;
1306 } else {
1307 context->ReportError(
1308 context, "The LSTM Full kernel expects 20 or 24 inputs. Got %d inputs",
1309 node->inputs->size);
1310 return kTfLiteError;
1311 }
1312
1313 const bool use_layer_norm = op_data->use_layer_norm;
1314
1315 // Inferring batch size, number of outputs and number of cells from the
1316 // input tensors.
1317 const TfLiteTensor* input;
1318 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputTensor, &input));
1319 const bool is_integer = input->type == kTfLiteInt8;
1320 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, input->dims->size > 1);
1321 const int n_batch = input->dims->data[0];
1322 const int n_input = input->dims->data[1];
1323
1324 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_output_weights;
1325 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1326 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToOutputWeightsTensor,
1327 &input_to_output_weights));
1328 const int n_cell = input_to_output_weights->dims->data[0];
1329 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_output_weights->dims->size, 2);
1330 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input_to_output_weights->dims->data[1], n_input);
1331
1332 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_output_weights;
1333 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1334 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToOutputWeightsTensor,
1335 &recurrent_to_output_weights));
1336 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_output_weights->dims->size, 2);
1337 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, recurrent_to_output_weights->dims->data[0],
1338 n_cell);
1339 const int n_output = recurrent_to_output_weights->dims->data[1];
1340
1341 // Check that input tensor dimensions matches with each other.
1342 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1343 context, CheckInputTensorDimensions(context, node, n_input, n_output,
1344 n_cell, use_layer_norm, is_integer));
1345
1346 // Get the pointer to output, output_state and cell_state tensors.
1347 TfLiteTensor* output;
1348 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1349 GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputTensor, &output));
1350
1351 TfLiteTensor* output_state =
1352 GetVariableInput(context, node, kOutputStateTensor);
1353 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, output_state != nullptr);
1354 TfLiteTensor* cell_state = GetVariableInput(context, node, kCellStateTensor);
1355 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, cell_state != nullptr);
1356
1357 // Check the shape of input state tensors.
1358 // These tensor may be 1D or 2D. It's fine as long as the total size is
1359 // correct.
1360 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, NumElements(output_state), n_batch * n_output);
1361 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, NumElements(cell_state), n_batch * n_cell);
1362
1363 // Resize the output tensors.
1364 TfLiteIntArray* output_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(2);
1365 output_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1366 output_size->data[1] = n_output;
1367 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1368 context->ResizeTensor(context, output, output_size));
1369
1370 // The weights are of consistent type, so it suffices to check one.
1371 const bool is_hybrid_op = IsHybridOp(input, input_to_output_weights);
1372
1373 const bool is_sparse_op = (input_to_output_weights->sparsity != nullptr);
1374
1375 // The type of Integer LSTM.
1376 const int num_intermediate_tensors = node->intermediates->size;
1377 if (is_integer) {
1378 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, num_intermediate_tensors == 5 ||
1379 num_intermediate_tensors == 12);
1380 }
1381 // We use number of intermediate tensors to distinguish the 8 bit matmul
1382 // output and the 16 bit matmul output version.
1383 const bool is_8x8_16 = num_intermediate_tensors == 5;
1384
1385 TfLiteIntArrayFree(node->temporaries);
1386 if (is_hybrid_op) {
1387 if (is_sparse_op) {
1388 node->temporaries =
1389 TfLiteIntArrayCreate(kNumHybridTemporaryTensors + kLedgersToAdd);
1390 } else {
1391 node->temporaries = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(kNumHybridTemporaryTensors);
1392 }
1393 } else if (is_integer) {
1394 if (is_8x8_16) {
1395 node->temporaries = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(6);
1396 } else {
1397 node->temporaries = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(8);
1398 }
1399 } else {
1400 node->temporaries = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(1);
1401 }
1402
1403 // Create a scratch buffer tensor for float case and hybrid case.
1404 // TODO(b/152066492): Create a is_float boolean and reorganize the temporary
1405 // buffer allocation logic.
1406 if (!is_integer) {
1407 node->temporaries->data[kScratchBuffer] =
1408 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kScratchBuffer;
1409 TfLiteTensor* scratch_buffer;
1410 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kScratchBuffer,
1411 &scratch_buffer));
1412 scratch_buffer->type = input->type;
1413 scratch_buffer->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1414
1415 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights =
1416 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputToInputWeightsTensor);
1417 const bool use_cifg = (input_to_input_weights == nullptr);
1418 TfLiteIntArray* scratch_buffer_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(2);
1419 scratch_buffer_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1420 if (use_cifg) {
1421 // Reserving space for Cell, Forget, Output gates
1422 scratch_buffer_size->data[1] = n_cell * 3;
1423 } else {
1424 // Reserving space for Input, Cell, Forget, Output gates
1425 scratch_buffer_size->data[1] = n_cell * 4;
1426 }
1427 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, context->ResizeTensor(context, scratch_buffer,
1428 scratch_buffer_size));
1429 }
1430
1431 if (is_hybrid_op) {
1432 if (!is_sparse_op) {
1433 op_data->compute_row_sums = true;
1434 }
1435 // Allocate temporary tensors to store quantized values of input,
1436 // output_state and cell_state tensors.
1437 node->temporaries->data[kInputQuantized] =
1438 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kInputQuantized;
1439 TfLiteTensor* input_quantized;
1440 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kInputQuantized,
1441 &input_quantized));
1442 input_quantized->type = input_to_output_weights->type;
1443 input_quantized->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1444 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqual(input_quantized->dims, input->dims)) {
1445 TfLiteIntArray* input_quantized_size = TfLiteIntArrayCopy(input->dims);
1446 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, context->ResizeTensor(context, input_quantized,
1447 input_quantized_size));
1448 }
1449 node->temporaries->data[kOutputStateQuantized] =
1450 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kOutputStateQuantized;
1451 TfLiteTensor* output_state_quantized;
1452 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1453 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kOutputStateQuantized,
1454 &output_state_quantized));
1455 output_state_quantized->type = input_to_output_weights->type;
1456 output_state_quantized->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1457 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqual(output_state_quantized->dims,
1458 output_state->dims)) {
1459 TfLiteIntArray* output_state_quantized_size =
1460 TfLiteIntArrayCopy(output_state->dims);
1461 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1462 context->ResizeTensor(context, output_state_quantized,
1463 output_state_quantized_size));
1464 }
1465 node->temporaries->data[kCellStateQuantized] =
1466 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kCellStateQuantized;
1467 TfLiteTensor* cell_state_quantized;
1468 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1469 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kCellStateQuantized,
1470 &cell_state_quantized));
1471 cell_state_quantized->type = input_to_output_weights->type;
1472 cell_state_quantized->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1473 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqual(cell_state_quantized->dims, cell_state->dims)) {
1474 TfLiteIntArray* cell_state_quantized_size =
1475 TfLiteIntArrayCopy(cell_state->dims);
1476 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1477 context->ResizeTensor(context, cell_state_quantized,
1478 cell_state_quantized_size));
1479 }
1480 // Allocate temporary tensors to store scaling factors and product scaling
1481 // factors. The latter is a convenience storage which allows to quantize
1482 // a vector once (which produces the scaling factors) and multiply it with
1483 // different matrices (which requires multiplying the scaling factors with
1484 // the scaling factor of the matrix).
1485 node->temporaries->data[kInputScalingFactors] =
1486 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kInputScalingFactors;
1487 TfLiteTensor* input_sf;
1488 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1489 context,
1490 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kInputScalingFactors, &input_sf));
1491 input_sf->type = kTfLiteFloat32;
1492 input_sf->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1493 int scaling_dims[1] = {n_batch};
1494 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(input_sf->dims, 1, scaling_dims)) {
1495 TfLiteIntArray* input_sf_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(1);
1496 input_sf_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1497 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1498 context, context->ResizeTensor(context, input_sf, input_sf_size));
1499 }
1500 node->temporaries->data[kOutputStateScalingFactors] =
1501 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kOutputStateScalingFactors;
1502 TfLiteTensor* output_state_sf;
1503 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1504 context, GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kOutputStateScalingFactors,
1505 &output_state_sf));
1506 output_state_sf->type = kTfLiteFloat32;
1507 output_state_sf->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1508 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(output_state_sf->dims, 1, scaling_dims)) {
1509 TfLiteIntArray* output_state_sf_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(1);
1510 output_state_sf_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1511 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, context->ResizeTensor(context, output_state_sf,
1512 output_state_sf_size));
1513 }
1514 node->temporaries->data[kProductScalingFactors] =
1515 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kProductScalingFactors;
1516 TfLiteTensor* prod_scaling_factors;
1517 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1518 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kProductScalingFactors,
1519 &prod_scaling_factors));
1520 prod_scaling_factors->type = kTfLiteFloat32;
1521 prod_scaling_factors->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1522 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(prod_scaling_factors->dims, 1,
1523 scaling_dims)) {
1524 TfLiteIntArray* prod_scaling_factors_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(1);
1525 prod_scaling_factors_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1526 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1527 context->ResizeTensor(context, prod_scaling_factors,
1528 prod_scaling_factors_size));
1529 }
1530
1531 // Allocate a temporary tensor to store the recovered cell weights. Since
1532 // this is used for diagonal matrices, only need to store n_cell values.
1533 node->temporaries->data[kRecoveredCellWeights] =
1534 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kRecoveredCellWeights;
1535 TfLiteTensor* recovered_cell_weights;
1536 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1537 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kRecoveredCellWeights,
1538 &recovered_cell_weights));
1539 recovered_cell_weights->type = kTfLiteFloat32;
1540 recovered_cell_weights->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1541 int recovered_cell_dims[1] = {n_cell};
1542 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(recovered_cell_weights->dims, 1,
1543 recovered_cell_dims)) {
1544 TfLiteIntArray* recovered_cell_weights_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(1);
1545 recovered_cell_weights_size->data[0] = n_cell;
1546 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1547 context->ResizeTensor(context, recovered_cell_weights,
1548 recovered_cell_weights_size));
1549 }
1550 // Allocate a temporary tensor to store accumulate values for matrix
1551 // multiplication before multiplication by scaling factor
1552 node->temporaries->data[kAccumScratch] =
1553 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kAccumScratch;
1554 TfLiteTensor* accum_scratch;
1555 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kAccumScratch,
1556 &accum_scratch));
1557 accum_scratch->type = kTfLiteInt32;
1558 accum_scratch->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1559 int accum_scratch_dims[2] = {n_cell, n_batch};
1560 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(accum_scratch->dims, 2,
1561 accum_scratch_dims)) {
1562 TfLiteIntArray* accum_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(2);
1563 accum_size->data[0] = n_cell;
1564 accum_size->data[1] = n_batch;
1565 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1566 context, context->ResizeTensor(context, accum_scratch, accum_size));
1567 }
1568 node->temporaries->data[kInputZeroPoints] =
1569 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kInputZeroPoints;
1570 TfLiteTensor* input_zp;
1571 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1572 context, GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kInputZeroPoints, &input_zp));
1573 input_zp->type = kTfLiteFloat32;
1574 input_zp->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1575 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(input_zp->dims, 1, scaling_dims)) {
1576 TfLiteIntArray* input_zp_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(1);
1577 input_zp_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1578 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1579 context, context->ResizeTensor(context, input_zp, input_zp_size));
1580 }
1581 node->temporaries->data[kOutputStateZeroPoints] =
1582 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kOutputStateZeroPoints;
1583 TfLiteTensor* output_state_zp;
1584 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1585 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kOutputStateZeroPoints,
1586 &output_state_zp));
1587 output_state_zp->type = kTfLiteFloat32;
1588 output_state_zp->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1589 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(output_state_zp->dims, 1, scaling_dims)) {
1590 TfLiteIntArray* output_state_zp_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(1);
1591 output_state_zp_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1592 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, context->ResizeTensor(context, output_state_zp,
1593 output_state_zp_size));
1594 }
1595
1596 node->temporaries->data[kRowSums] =
1597 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + kRowSums;
1598 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights =
1599 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputToInputWeightsTensor);
1600 const bool use_cifg = (input_to_input_weights == nullptr);
1601 int row_sums_rows = use_cifg ? 6 : 8;
1602 const TfLiteTensor* projection_weights =
1603 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionWeightsTensor);
1604 if (projection_weights != nullptr) {
1605 row_sums_rows += ceil(static_cast<float>(n_output) / n_cell);
1606 }
1607
1608 TfLiteTensor* row_sums;
1609 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1610 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kRowSums, &row_sums));
1611 row_sums->type = kTfLiteInt32;
1612 row_sums->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRwPersistent;
1613 const int row_sums_dims[2] = {row_sums_rows, n_cell};
1614 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(row_sums->dims, 2, row_sums_dims)) {
1615 TfLiteIntArray* row_sums_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(2);
1616 row_sums_size->data[0] = row_sums_dims[0];
1617 row_sums_size->data[1] = row_sums_dims[1];
1618 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1619 context, context->ResizeTensor(context, row_sums, row_sums_size));
1620 }
1621
1622 if (is_sparse_op) {
1623 op_data->ledger_initialized = false;
1624 int offset = kNumHybridTemporaryTensors;
1625 {
1626 node->temporaries->data[offset + kInputToInputWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1627 op_data->ledger_index + kInputToInputWeightsLedgerOffset;
1628 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights =
1629 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputToInputWeightsTensor);
1630 TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights_ledger =
1631 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1632 kInputToInputWeightsLedgerOffset];
1633 auto status = make_ledger(input_to_input_weights == nullptr
1634 ? nullptr
1635 : input_to_input_weights->sparsity,
1636 context, input_to_input_weights_ledger);
1637 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1638 }
1639 {
1640 node->temporaries->data[offset + kInputToForgetWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1641 op_data->ledger_index + kInputToForgetWeightsLedgerOffset;
1642 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_forget_weights =
1643 GetInput(context, node, kInputToForgetWeightsTensor);
1644 TfLiteTensor* input_to_forget_weights_ledger =
1645 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1646 kInputToForgetWeightsLedgerOffset];
1647 auto status = make_ledger(input_to_forget_weights->sparsity, context,
1648 input_to_forget_weights_ledger);
1649 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1650 }
1651 {
1652 node->temporaries->data[offset + kInputToCellWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1653 op_data->ledger_index + kInputToCellWeightsLedgerOffset;
1654 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_cell_weights =
1655 GetInput(context, node, kInputToCellWeightsTensor);
1656 TfLiteTensor* input_to_cell_weights_ledger =
1657 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1658 kInputToCellWeightsLedgerOffset];
1659 auto status = make_ledger(input_to_cell_weights->sparsity, context,
1660 input_to_cell_weights_ledger);
1661 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1662 }
1663 {
1664 node->temporaries->data[offset + kInputToOutputWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1665 op_data->ledger_index + kInputToOutputWeightsLedgerOffset;
1666 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_output_weights =
1667 GetInput(context, node, kInputToOutputWeightsTensor);
1668 TfLiteTensor* input_to_output_weights_ledger =
1669 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1670 kInputToOutputWeightsLedgerOffset];
1671 auto status = make_ledger(input_to_output_weights->sparsity, context,
1672 input_to_output_weights_ledger);
1673 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1674 }
1675 {
1676 node->temporaries->data[offset + kRecurrentToInputWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1677 op_data->ledger_index + kRecurrentToInputWeightsLedgerOffset;
1678 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_input_weights = GetOptionalInputTensor(
1679 context, node, kRecurrentToInputWeightsTensor);
1680 TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_input_weights_ledger =
1681 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1682 kRecurrentToInputWeightsLedgerOffset];
1683 auto status = make_ledger(recurrent_to_input_weights == nullptr
1684 ? nullptr
1685 : recurrent_to_input_weights->sparsity,
1686 context, recurrent_to_input_weights_ledger);
1687 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1688 }
1689 {
1690 node->temporaries
1691 ->data[offset + kRecurrentToForgetWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1692 op_data->ledger_index + kRecurrentToForgetWeightsLedgerOffset;
1693 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_forget_weights =
1694 GetInput(context, node, kRecurrentToForgetWeightsTensor);
1695 TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_forget_weights_ledger =
1696 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1697 kRecurrentToForgetWeightsLedgerOffset];
1698 auto status = make_ledger(recurrent_to_forget_weights->sparsity,
1699 context, recurrent_to_forget_weights_ledger);
1700 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1701 }
1702 {
1703 node->temporaries->data[offset + kRecurrentToCellWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1704 op_data->ledger_index + kRecurrentToCellWeightsLedgerOffset;
1705 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_cell_weights =
1706 GetInput(context, node, kRecurrentToCellWeightsTensor);
1707 TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_cell_weights_ledger =
1708 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1709 kRecurrentToCellWeightsLedgerOffset];
1710 auto status = make_ledger(recurrent_to_cell_weights->sparsity, context,
1711 recurrent_to_cell_weights_ledger);
1712 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1713 }
1714 {
1715 node->temporaries
1716 ->data[offset + kRecurrentToOutputWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1717 op_data->ledger_index + kRecurrentToOutputWeightsLedgerOffset;
1718 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_output_weights =
1719 GetInput(context, node, kRecurrentToOutputWeightsTensor);
1720 TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_output_weights_ledger =
1721 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1722 kRecurrentToOutputWeightsLedgerOffset];
1723 auto status = make_ledger(recurrent_to_output_weights->sparsity,
1724 context, recurrent_to_output_weights_ledger);
1725 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1726 }
1727 {
1728 node->temporaries->data[offset + kProjectionWeightsLedgerOffset] =
1729 op_data->ledger_index + kProjectionWeightsLedgerOffset;
1730 const TfLiteTensor* projection_weights =
1731 GetInput(context, node, kProjectionWeightsTensor);
1732 TfLiteTensor* projection_weights_ledger =
1733 &context->tensors[op_data->ledger_index +
1734 kProjectionWeightsLedgerOffset];
1735 auto status = make_ledger(projection_weights->sparsity, context,
1736 projection_weights_ledger);
1737 if (status != kTfLiteOk) return status;
1738 }
1739 }
1740 }
1741
1742 if (is_integer) {
1743 if (is_8x8_16) {
1744 // Integer LSTM prepare function for 8x8->16.
1745 // This code path needs 5 intermediate tensors per Op.
1746 // Populate quantization parameters.
1747 PopulateQuantizedLstmParams8x8_16(context, node,
1748 &op_data->integer_lstm_param);
1749
1750 // Allocate scratch buffer. Need 6 16bit buffer with size n_batch * n_cell
1751 // and 1 8bit buffer with size n_batch * n_cell. We also need 1 32 bit
1752 // buffer with size n_batch * n_cell.
1753 //
1754 // Handle cifg case as well, which might save one buffer.
1755 for (int scratch_index = 0; scratch_index < 6; ++scratch_index) {
1756 node->temporaries->data[scratch_index] =
1757 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + scratch_index;
1758 TfLiteTensor* scratch_tensor;
1759 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1760 context,
1761 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, scratch_index, &scratch_tensor));
1762 scratch_tensor->type = kTfLiteInt16;
1763 if (scratch_index == 4) {
1764 scratch_tensor->type = kTfLiteInt8;
1765 } else if (scratch_index == 5) {
1766 scratch_tensor->type = kTfLiteInt32;
1767 }
1768 scratch_tensor->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1769 const int scratch_dimension[2] = {n_batch, n_cell};
1770 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(scratch_tensor->dims, 2,
1771 scratch_dimension)) {
1772 TfLiteIntArray* scratch_buffer_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(2);
1773 scratch_buffer_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1774 scratch_buffer_size->data[1] = n_cell;
1775 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1776 context->ResizeTensor(context, scratch_tensor,
1777 scratch_buffer_size));
1778 }
1779 }
1780
1781 // Populate precomputed zp * weight.
1782 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, PopulatePrecomputedZPTimesWeightsWithBias(
1783 context, op_data, node));
1784 } else {
1785 // Integer LSTM prepare function for 8x8->8.
1786 // This code path needs 12 intermediate tensors per Op.
1787 PopulateQuantizedLstmParams8x8_8(context, node,
1788 &op_data->integer_lstm_param);
1789
1790 // Allocate scratch buffer. Need 6 16bit buffer with size n_batch * n_cell
1791 // and 2 8bit buffer with size n_batch * n_cell.
1792 //
1793 // Handle cifg case as well, which might save one buffer.
1794 for (int scratch_index = 0; scratch_index < 8; ++scratch_index) {
1795 node->temporaries->data[scratch_index] =
1796 op_data->scratch_tensor_index + scratch_index;
1797 TfLiteTensor* scratch_tensor;
1798 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
1799 context,
1800 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, scratch_index, &scratch_tensor));
1801 if (scratch_index == 0 || scratch_index == 1) {
1802 scratch_tensor->type = kTfLiteInt8;
1803 } else {
1804 scratch_tensor->type = kTfLiteInt16;
1805 }
1806 scratch_tensor->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRw;
1807 const int scratch_dimension[2] = {n_batch, n_cell};
1808 if (!TfLiteIntArrayEqualsArray(scratch_tensor->dims, 2,
1809 scratch_dimension)) {
1810 TfLiteIntArray* scratch_buffer_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(2);
1811 scratch_buffer_size->data[0] = n_batch;
1812 scratch_buffer_size->data[1] = n_cell;
1813 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1814 context->ResizeTensor(context, scratch_tensor,
1815 scratch_buffer_size));
1816 }
1817 }
1818 }
1819 }
1820 return kTfLiteOk;
1821}
1822// LINT.ThenChange(//tensorflow/lite/tools/optimize/calibration/builtin_logging_ops/lstm.cc)
1823
1824// LINT.IfChange
1825TfLiteStatus Eval(TfLiteContext* context, TfLiteNode* node) {
1826 const auto* params = static_cast<TfLiteLSTMParams*>(node->builtin_data);
1827 OpData* op_data = static_cast<OpData*>(node->user_data);
1828
1829 const TfLiteTensor* input;
1830 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputTensor, &input));
1831
1832 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_input_weights =
1833 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputToInputWeightsTensor);
1834 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_forget_weights;
1835 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1836 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToForgetWeightsTensor,
1837 &input_to_forget_weights));
1838 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_cell_weights;
1839 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1840 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToCellWeightsTensor,
1841 &input_to_cell_weights));
1842 const TfLiteTensor* input_to_output_weights;
1843 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1844 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputToOutputWeightsTensor,
1845 &input_to_output_weights));
1846
1847 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_input_weights =
1848 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kRecurrentToInputWeightsTensor);
1849 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_forget_weights;
1850 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1851 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToForgetWeightsTensor,
1852 &recurrent_to_forget_weights));
1853 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_cell_weights;
1854 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1855 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToCellWeightsTensor,
1856 &recurrent_to_cell_weights));
1857 const TfLiteTensor* recurrent_to_output_weights;
1858 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
