1859 GetInputSafe(context, node, kRecurrentToOutputWeightsTensor,
1860 &recurrent_to_output_weights));
1861
1862 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_input_weights =
1863 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToInputWeightsTensor);
1864 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_forget_weights =
1865 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToForgetWeightsTensor);
1866 const TfLiteTensor* cell_to_output_weights =
1867 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellToOutputWeightsTensor);
1868
1869 const TfLiteTensor* input_layer_norm_coefficients =
1870 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1871 const TfLiteTensor* forget_layer_norm_coefficients =
1872 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kForgetLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1873 const TfLiteTensor* cell_layer_norm_coefficients =
1874 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kCellLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1875 const TfLiteTensor* output_layer_norm_coefficients =
1876 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kOutputLayerNormCoefficientsTensor);
1877
1878 const TfLiteTensor* input_gate_bias =
1879 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kInputGateBiasTensor);
1880 const TfLiteTensor* forget_gate_bias;
1881 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kForgetGateBiasTensor,
1882 &forget_gate_bias));
1883 const TfLiteTensor* cell_gate_bias;
1884 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kCellGateBiasTensor,
1885 &cell_gate_bias));
1886 const TfLiteTensor* output_gate_bias;
1887 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kOutputGateBiasTensor,
1888 &output_gate_bias));
1889
1890 const TfLiteTensor* projection_weights =
1891 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionWeightsTensor);
1892 const TfLiteTensor* projection_bias =
1893 GetOptionalInputTensor(context, node, kProjectionBiasTensor);
1894
1895 TfLiteTensor* output_state =
1896 GetVariableInput(context, node, kOutputStateTensor);
1897 TFLITE_DCHECK(output_state != nullptr);
1898 TfLiteTensor* cell_state = GetVariableInput(context, node, kCellStateTensor);
1899 TFLITE_DCHECK(cell_state != nullptr);
1900
1901 TfLiteTensor* output;
1902 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1903 GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputTensor, &output));
1904
1905 switch (input_to_output_weights->type) {
1906 case kTfLiteFloat32: {
1907 // Index the scratch buffers pointers to the global scratch buffer.
1908 TfLiteTensor* scratch_buffer;
1909 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1910 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, 0, &scratch_buffer));
1911 return lstm_eval::EvalFloat(
1912 input, input_to_input_weights, input_to_forget_weights,
1913 input_to_cell_weights, input_to_output_weights,
1914 recurrent_to_input_weights, recurrent_to_forget_weights,
1915 recurrent_to_cell_weights, recurrent_to_output_weights,
1916 cell_to_input_weights, cell_to_forget_weights, cell_to_output_weights,
1917 input_layer_norm_coefficients, forget_layer_norm_coefficients,
1918 cell_layer_norm_coefficients, output_layer_norm_coefficients,
1919 /*aux_input=*/nullptr,
1920 /*aux_input_to_input_weights=*/nullptr,
1921 /*aux_input_to_forget_weights=*/nullptr,
1922 /*aux_input_to_cell_weights=*/nullptr,
1923 /*aux_input_to_output_weights=*/nullptr, input_gate_bias,
1924 forget_gate_bias, cell_gate_bias, output_gate_bias,
1925 projection_weights, projection_bias, params,
1926 /*forward_sequence=*/true,
1927 /*time_major=*/true,
1928 /*output_offset=*/0, scratch_buffer, output_state, cell_state,
1929 output);
1930 }
1931 case kTfLiteUInt8:
1932 case kTfLiteInt8: {
1933 const bool is_hybrid = (input->type == kTfLiteFloat32);
1934 const bool is_sparse = input_to_output_weights->sparsity != nullptr;
1935 if (is_hybrid) {
1936 TfLiteTensor* row_sums;
1937 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
1938 GetTemporarySafe(context, node, kRowSums, &row_sums));
1939 const int row_sums_size = row_sums->dims->data[0];
1940 if (is_sparse) {

2190TfLiteStatus Prepare(TfLiteContext* context, TfLiteNode* node) {
2191 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, node->inputs->size == kInputNum);
2192 TF_LITE_ENSURE(context, node->outputs->size == kOutputNum);
2193
2194 const TfLiteTensor* input;
2195 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputData, &input));
2196 const TfLiteTensor* prev_activation;
2197 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputPrevActivation,
2198 &prev_activation));
2199 const TfLiteTensor* weights;
2200 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
2201 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputWeights, &weights));
2202 const TfLiteTensor* bias;
2203 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputBiases, &bias));
2204 const TfLiteTensor* prev_state;
2205 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
2206 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputPrevState, &prev_state));
2207
2208 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, input->dims->size, 2);
2209 const int num_batches = input->dims->data[0];
2210 const int input_depth = input->dims->data[1];
2211
2212 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, prev_activation->dims->size, 2);
2213 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, prev_activation->dims->data[0], num_batches);
2214 const int activation_depth = prev_activation->dims->data[1];
2215 const int total_depth = input_depth + activation_depth;
2216
2217 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, weights->dims->size, 2);
2218 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, weights->dims->data[0], 4 * activation_depth);
2219 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, weights->dims->data[1], total_depth);
2220
2221 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, bias->dims->size, 1);
2222 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, bias->dims->data[0], 4 * activation_depth);
2223
2224 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, prev_state->dims->size, 2);
2225 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, prev_state->dims->data[0], num_batches);
2226 TF_LITE_ENSURE_EQ(context, prev_state->dims->data[1], activation_depth);
2227
2228 TfLiteTensor* activation_out;
2229 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputActivation,
2230 &activation_out));
2231 TfLiteTensor* state_out;
2232 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
2233 GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputState, &state_out));
2234 TfLiteTensor* concat_temp;
2235 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
2236 context, GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputConcatTemp, &concat_temp));
2237 TfLiteTensor* activation_temp;
2238 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputActivationTemp,
2239 &activation_temp));
2240
2241 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, context->ResizeTensor(
2242 context, activation_out,
2243 TfLiteIntArrayCopy(prev_activation->dims)));
2244 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
2245 context, context->ResizeTensor(context, state_out,
2246 TfLiteIntArrayCopy(prev_state->dims)));
2247
2248 TfLiteIntArray* concat_temp_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(2);
2249 concat_temp_size->data[0] = num_batches;
2250 concat_temp_size->data[1] = total_depth;
2251 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
2252 context, context->ResizeTensor(context, concat_temp, concat_temp_size));
2253 TfLiteIntArray* activation_temp_size = TfLiteIntArrayCreate(2);
2254 activation_temp_size->data[0] = num_batches;
2255 activation_temp_size->data[1] = 4 * activation_depth;
2256 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, context->ResizeTensor(context, activation_temp,
2257 activation_temp_size));
2258
2259 // Set the state tensors as persistent.
2260 for (auto index : {kInputPrevActivation, kInputPrevState}) {
2261 TfLiteTensor* tensor = &context->tensors[node->inputs->data[index]];
2262 tensor->allocation_type = kTfLiteArenaRwPersistent;
2263 }
2264 return kTfLiteOk;
2265}

2267TfLiteStatus Eval(TfLiteContext* context, TfLiteNode* node) {
2268 const TfLiteTensor* input;
2269 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputData, &input));
2270 const TfLiteTensor* prev_activation;
2271 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputPrevActivation,
2272 &prev_activation));
2273 const TfLiteTensor* weights;
2274 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
2275 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputWeights, &weights));
2276 const TfLiteTensor* bias;
2277 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputBiases, &bias));
2278 const TfLiteTensor* prev_state;
2279 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
2280 GetInputSafe(context, node, kInputPrevState, &prev_state));
2281
2282 TfLiteTensor* activation_out;
2283 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputActivation,
2284 &activation_out));
2285 TfLiteTensor* state_out;
2286 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context,
2287 GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputState, &state_out));
2288 TfLiteTensor* concat_temp;
2289 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(
2290 context, GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputConcatTemp, &concat_temp));
2291 TfLiteTensor* activation_temp;
2292 TF_LITE_ENSURE_OK(context, GetOutputSafe(context, node, kOutputActivationTemp,
2293 &activation_temp));
2294
2295 if (input->type == kTfLiteFloat32 &&
2296 prev_activation->type == kTfLiteFloat32 &&
2297 weights->type == kTfLiteFloat32 && bias->type == kTfLiteFloat32 &&
2298 prev_state->type == kTfLiteFloat32 && state_out->type == kTfLiteFloat32 &&
2299 activation_out->type == kTfLiteFloat32 &&
2300 concat_temp->type == kTfLiteFloat32 &&
2301 activation_temp->type == kTfLiteFloat32) {
2302 tflite::LstmCellParams op_params;
2303 // Float LSTM cell does not need parameters to be set: leave untouched.
2304 optimized_ops::LstmCell(
2305 op_params,
2306 // Inputs.
2307 GetTensorShape(input), GetTensorData<float>(input),
2308 GetTensorShape(prev_activation), GetTensorData<float>(prev_activation),
2309 GetTensorShape(weights), GetTensorData<float>(weights),
2310 GetTensorShape(bias), GetTensorData<float>(bias),
2311 GetTensorShape(prev_state), GetTensorData<float>(prev_state),
2312 // Outputs.
2313 GetTensorShape(state_out), GetTensorData<float>(state_out),
2314 GetTensorShape(activation_out), GetTensorData<float>(activation_out),
2315 GetTensorShape(concat_temp), GetTensorData<float>(concat_temp),
2316 GetTensorShape(activation_temp), GetTensorData<float>(activation_temp),
2317 CpuBackendContext::GetFromContext(context));
2318 } else if (input->type == kTfLiteUInt8 &&
2319 prev_activation->type == kTfLiteUInt8 &&
2320 weights->type == kTfLiteUInt8 && bias->type == kTfLiteInt32 &&
2321 prev_state->type == kTfLiteInt16 &&
2322 state_out->type == kTfLiteInt16 &&
2323 activation_out->type == kTfLiteUInt8 &&
2324 concat_temp->type == kTfLiteUInt8 &&
2325 activation_temp->type == kTfLiteInt16) {
2326 int state_scale_log2_rounded;
2327 if (!CheckedLog2(state_out->params.scale, &state_scale_log2_rounded)) {
2328 context->ReportError(
2329 context,
2330 "The internal state of a LSTM cell must have a power-of-two scale.");
2331 return kTfLiteError;
2332 }
2333 const int state_integer_bits = 15 + state_scale_log2_rounded;
2334 if (state_integer_bits != 4) {
2335 context->ReportError(context,
2336 "The only case of quantized LstmCell currently "
2337 "supported is with StateIntegerBits==4");
2338 return kTfLiteError;
2339 }
2340
2341 double real_accum_multiplier = 4096 * bias->params.scale;
2342 int32 accum_multiplier;
2343 int accum_shift;
2344 tflite::QuantizeMultiplier(real_accum_multiplier, &accum_multiplier,
2345 &accum_shift);
2346 tflite::LstmCellParams op_params;
2347 op_params.weights_zero_point = weights->params.zero_point;
2348 op_params.accum_multiplier = accum_multiplier;
2349 op_params.accum_shift = accum_shift;
2350 optimized_ops::LstmCell<4>(
2351 op_params,
2352 // Inputs.
2353 GetTensorShape(input), GetTensorData<uint8_t>(input),
2354 GetTensorShape(prev_activation),
2355 GetTensorData<uint8_t>(prev_activation), GetTensorShape(weights),
2356 GetTensorData<uint8_t>(weights), GetTensorShape(bias),
2357 GetTensorData<int32_t>(bias), GetTensorShape(prev_state),
2358 GetTensorData<int16_t>(prev_state),
2359 // Outputs.
2360 GetTensorShape(state_out), GetTensorData<int16_t>(state_out),
2361 GetTensorShape(activation_out), GetTensorData<uint8_t>(activation_out),
2362 GetTensorShape(concat_temp), GetTensorData<uint8_t>(concat_temp),
2363 GetTensorShape(activation_temp),
2364 GetTensorData<int16_t>(activation_temp),
2365 CpuBackendContext::GetFromContext(context));
2366 } else {
2367 context->ReportError(context,
2368 "Unsupported combination of data types for LstmCell");
2369 return kTfLiteError;
2370 }
2371
2372 // TODO(ycling): Investigate if this copy can be avoided with the 5-inputs
2373 // LSTM kernel.
2374 memcpy(prev_activation->data.raw, activation_out->data.raw,
2375 activation_out->bytes);
2376 memcpy(prev_state->data.raw, state_out->data.raw, state_out->bytes);
2377
2378 return kTfLiteOk;
2379}

2383void* Init(TfLiteContext* context, const char* buffer, size_t length) {
2384 const auto* params = reinterpret_cast<const TfLiteLSTMParams*>(buffer);
2385 switch (params->kernel_type) {
2386 case kTfLiteLSTMFullKernel:
2387 return full::Init(context, buffer, length);
2388 case kTfLiteLSTMBasicKernel:
2389 return basic::Init(context, buffer, length);
2390 default:
2391 return nullptr;
2392 }
2393 return nullptr;
2394}
2395void Free(TfLiteContext* context, void* buffer) {
2396 delete static_cast<OpData*>(buffer);
2397}
2398
2399TfLiteStatus Prepare(TfLiteContext* context, TfLiteNode* node) {
2400 const auto* op_data = static_cast<const OpData*>(node->user_data);
2401 switch (op_data->kernel_type) {
2402 case kTfLiteLSTMFullKernel:
2403 return full::Prepare(context, node);
2404 case kTfLiteLSTMBasicKernel:
2405 return basic::Prepare(context, node);
2406 default:
2407 return kTfLiteError;
2408 }
2409 return kTfLiteError;
2410}
2411
2412TfLiteStatus Eval(TfLiteContext* context, TfLiteNode* node) {
2413 const auto* op_data = static_cast<const OpData*>(node->user_data);
2414 switch (op_data->kernel_type) {
2415 case kTfLiteLSTMFullKernel:
2416 return full::Eval(context, node);
2417 case kTfLiteLSTMBasicKernel:
2418 return basic::Eval(context, node);
2419 default:
2420 return kTfLiteError;
2421 }
2422 return kTfLiteError;
2423}
